tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE program_impact (
    program_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    program_name VARCHAR(255),
    impact_type VARCHAR(50),
    impact_description TEXT,
    awareness_level INT,
    advocacy_level INT
)

CREATE TABLE Program (
    program_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    program_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    program_description TEXT,
    program_start_date DATE,
    program_end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE Participant (
    participant_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    first_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    last_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    email VARCHAR(255),
    start_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE Impact (
    impact_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    program_id INT REFERENCES Program(program_id),
    participant_id INT REFERENCES Participant(participant_id),
    impact_score INT,
    impact_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE impact_of_educational_programs (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    program_name VARCHAR(50),
    organization_name VARCHAR(50),
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE human_rights_awareness (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    participant_name VARCHAR(50),
    age INT,
    aware_level INT,
    program_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (program_id) REFERENCES impact_of_educational_programs(id)
);

CREATE TABLE advocacy_activities (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    activity_type VARCHAR(50),
    location VARCHAR(50),
    date DATE,
    participant_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (participant_id) REFERENCES human_rights_awareness(id)
);

CREATE TABLE program_evaluation (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    program_id INT,
    evaluator_name VARCHAR(50),
    evaluation_date DATE,
    evaluation_score INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (program_id) REFERENCES impact_of_educational_programs(id)
);

CREATE TABLE participant (
 participant_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
 participant_name VARCHAR(255),
 age INT,
 gender VARCHAR(10),
 program_id UUID REFERENCES program(program_id)
);

CREATE TABLE impact_measurement (
 measurement_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
 measurement_date DATE,
 awareness_level INT,
 advocacy_level INT,
 participant_id UUID REFERENCES participant(participant_id)
);
